Challenge

Class BFSVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • Challenge.BFSVertex

  • class BFSVertex
extends java.lang.Object
    A BFS Vertex contains the x coordinate, the y coordinate, and distance from the source node. This class is used in the Smart Enemy class which requires these fields to implement the wavefront planning algorithm. This is just a BFS search and from that, find the shortest path back to the starting node from the goal node.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Chuks
